{"tid":1667024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全城中計，全部注意力去曬清真寺到，冇人理會人權法同20/10義士。","createTime":"2019-10-21T08:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T11:03:34.000Z","uid":62011,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0e9a35daeee62e789e168600c3e862b485bb9faf","tid":1667024,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />引到大家入嚟就好。<br />\n<br />\n我想講清真寺單野要繼續發酵之餘，請唔好唔記得仲有人權法未過，未過之前要繼續去唔同參議院議員TWITTER遊說。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(行動POST) 今日既行動係眾議院議員感謝日 暨 參議員游說日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1657041\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1657041</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n美國人權及民主法案未正式通過<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656893\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656893</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二，20/10被捕義士冇人理，請大家多多留意。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跪求大家一齊搵加士居道手足搜尋/被捕消息<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666266</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n旺角即時現場,多人被捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665467</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4be9078e235f94c72857aab5c33071c9872604bf","tid":1667024,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:40:20.000Z","msg":"[突發]今晚18區都有野搞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666302</a>"},{"pid":"cbc2677aaa3d342d0c26bcea7097207ed8ddd1d1","tid":1667024,"uid":217542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:43:20.000Z","msg":"[突發] 北角好似有手足出事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665948\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665948</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n幫手推 冇媒體報導 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02f52fea470625c0bd4aca0836c71cde74c40d14","tid":1667024,"uid":49370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:48:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f87e52398e1b485abf1dd46006115eae8344f89d","tid":1667024,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:58:39.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"981daa418ad400e879d62e9acf12800e36ff02d3","tid":1667024,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:59:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a1c1e5cd659a5a3a1c5ebd025583dc6591246821","tid":1667024,"uid":37220,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:04:19.000Z","msg":"中你老母咩<br />\n最撚on9就係呢類topic"},{"pid":"1d8267ef7bb36164602a290b29fe4db134be630d","tid":1667024,"uid":137209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:06:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9cc59e28014f05deda53f121c4e9cc796fc9371","tid":1667024,"uid":194398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:03:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}